Waspinator turned his head to see the troops following him.
"Ha! Stupid bot will never catch Waspinator!  Waspinator too quick and 
smart for troop.  Waspi-"

impact then recoiled throwing Waspinator to the ground in the opposite 
direction.
"Waspinator not fell good."
